<%= currently_at 'Tasks' %>

<div class="topstatement">
	<% if member_signed_in? %>
		<% if @tasks == 0 %>
		Looks like we should add a few tasks, click the button below
		<% else %>
		Coolio.  Getting the hang of it.  Keep it up!  Winning!
		<% end %>
	<% else %>
		Below are actual tasks created and used by current members, become a member and create your own.  Here's the key - these are not basic everyday tasks, to get the most of these, reserve for those that are going to push you towards your goals and stretch you.  Go get 'em!
	<% end %>
</div>

<div class="topbanner">
    <% if member_signed_in? %>
        <%= link_to 'Add New Task', new_task_path, :method => 'get', :class => 'button-link' %>
    <% else %>
        <%= link_to 'Become a Member', new_member_registration_path, :class => 'button-link' %> and Create Your Own Tasks to Achieve!	
    <% end %>
</div>

